properties.name: dialogText
properties.value: Be careful while going south! A few goblins were spotted. These devilish creatures don't hesitate in throwing stones in whoever appears in front of them.

properties.name: dialogText
properties.value:
My name is Ragnok, and I am one of the guards here at the bank. My job is to keep the bank and its customers safe, so if you see anything suspicious or have any concerns, don't hesitate to let me know.

We take the security of the bank and its customers very seriously, and have implemented a number of measures to ensure the safety of everyone inside. We have guards stationed at every entrance and exit, as well as security measures such as traps and alarms to deter would-be thieves.

properties.name: dialogText
properties.value:
Welcome, traveler, to the heart of the Shadowlands. It is a place of darkness, but also of strength and resilience. Here, in the city's beating heart, we find a way to thrive.

I am Yagura, known as Gruumsha's Shaman. I serve as a spiritual guide for this city, providing wisdom and guidance to those who seek it.

You seem to bear a heavy burden. Tell me, wanderer, what brings you to our city cloaked in shadows?

properties.name: dialogText
properties.value:
Halt! I am Azruk Doomweaver of the Sacred Grove, sworn to protect this holy site from all who would profane it. This is a holy place, and it is not to be taken lightly. Show the proper respect and reverence at all times, and do not stray from the designated paths. 

Welcome to the shrine, traveler. May your stay here be peaceful and enlightening!

properties.name: dialogText
properties.value:
Welcome to our bank! My name is Freya Thunderhoof, and I am one of our bankers here. We offer a variety of financial services, including secure storage for your precious items, account management, loans, and investments.

If you need a safe place to store your valuable items or gold, we have a variety of storage options to suit your needs. We take great care in ensuring the security of our vaults, so you can rest assured that your items are safe with us.

properties.name: dialogText
properties.value:
Welcome to my humble food stall, traveler! My name is Lyra Stonemane, and I specialize in delicious street food that will satisfy your hunger on your journey. I have a variety of dishes to choose from, including savory meat pies, spicy kebabs, and sweet pastries.

All of my ingredients are fresh and locally sourced, and I take great pride in preparing each dish to perfection. If you're in a hurry, I have some pre-made meals ready to go, but if you have a little time to spare, I can prepare something fresh just for you.

properties.name: dialogText
properties.value:
Welcome to my forge, {{char.name}}. My name is Grommash Ironhorn, and I am the master blacksmith in these parts. What can I do for you today? Do you seek a sturdy sword to cleave through your enemies, a suit of armor to protect you from their blows, or perhaps some training equipment to hone your skills?

All of my wares are crafted with the finest materials and techniques, and I take great pride in the quality of my work. I am also skilled at repairs, so if your gear is in need of fixing, I am happy to take a look.

Take your time browsing my wares, and let me know if you have any questions or special requests. It would be my pleasure to assist you in your quest.

properties.name: dialogText
properties.value: Welcome to my training shop. I am Zorak Blackfeather, and I will be your instructor. Here, we do not simply learn how to wield a sword or fight. We learn how to master our bodies, our minds, and our spirits. We learn how to become true warriors.

properties.name: dialogText
properties.value:
Welcome to my shop, {{char.name}}! My name is Gorgrak Swiftshot, and I am a marksman specializing in ranged weapons. I offer a wide selection of weapons to suit your needs, including bows, arrows, slingshots, and more.

If you are in need of a new weapon, I highly recommend taking a look at my bows. Each bow is crafted with care and precision, using only the finest materials. And if you need ammunition, I have a variety of arrows and stones to choose from, including iron-tipped arrows for added piercing power.

properties.name: dialogText
properties.value: Ah, welcome to my tavern, dearie! My name is Grizznak Stormbrew, and I am the mistress of this fine establishment. What brings you in today? Are you looking for a cozy spot to warm yourself by the fire, or perhaps a refreshing ale to quench your thirst?

properties.name: dialogText
properties.value: Hello there, and welcome to my jewelry shop. My name is Durgak, and I am the owner. It's so lovely to have you here. What can I help you with today?

properties.name: dialogText
properties.value: Welcome to our mystical emporium, {{char.name}}! How may we assist you on your journey today? Are you in need of potent potions, powerful runes, or perhaps a new staff to aid in your magical endeavors?

properties.name: dialogText
properties.value: Welcome to my shop, my friend. I am Serena the Herbalist, and I am here to help you find whatever herbs or remedies you may need. How can I be of service to you today?

properties.name: dialogText
properties.value: Hey {{char.name}}, have you seen anything strange lately?

properties.name: dialogText
properties.value: Hey {{char.name}}! Be careful with the Ghouls, they can be very strong...

properties.name: dialogText
properties.value: Hey {{char.name}}, careful when going beyond the city walls. I heard Ghouls are settling nearby, planning a raid soon. Last time they burned the whole village down and we had to re-build what's left. These damn undeads!

properties.name: dialogText
properties.value: Hello {{char.name}}. Have you seen a lost lizard around here?
